##Intro

Email Extractor is a powerful email extension. It allows you to export emails from any page to a csv format file with just one click.

## Features
Automatic email search
Export selected emails in csv format
Export selected emails in csv format
Removing duplicate emails.

#It's free?

Yes, Email Extractor is free. You can get basic features and upgrade to get more features.
